<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.8">
<l>muṉṉai vaṇṇam pāliṉ vaṇṇam muḻutum nilainiṉṟa</l>
<l>piṉṉai vaṇṇaṅ koṇṭal vaṇṇam vaṇṇa meṇṇuṅkāl</l>
<l>poṉṉiṉ vaṇṇam maṇiyiṉ vaṇṇam puraiyun tirumēṉi</l>
<l>iṉṉa vaṇṇa meṉṟu kāṭṭī rinta ḷūrīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The previous color was the color of milk; the latter color was a cloud color,</l>
<l>Which has always remained [your] nature. When recounting colors,</l>
<l>You of Intaḷūr, show [us] such colors of [your] divine body</l>
<l>That [also] resembles a gold color and a [ruby] jewel color.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
